Package gov.sandia.cf.dao.migration.tasks

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Task_001_QoIITag
    Migration of QoI to manage tags on the QoI Home View.
    Task_002_RichTextContent
    Migration of fields to add richtext content and allow bigger content in the columns: from VARCHAR to LONGVARCHAR
    Task_003_PlanningFieldLongVarchar
    Migration of PCMM Planning and Uncertainty fields from VARCHAR to LONGVARCHAR.
    Task_004_GenericParameterRequired
    Import the generic parameters "isRequired" to "required" field changes.
    Task_005_ConfigurationFileTable
    Move the configuration files from the MODEL table into a specific table CONFIGURATION_FILE.
    Task_006_SystemRequirementStatementField
    Migrate Statement values from System Requirement Value to a persistent field within System Requirement: 1.
    Task_007_ARGParametersLongVarcharFields
    Migration of ARGParameters fields from VARCHAR to LONGVARCHAR
    Task_008_UnknownCreationUserXorDate
    Migration of entities where creation user is missing.
    Task_009_EvidenceValueToGson
    Migration of evidence values to Gson format including evidence type.
    Task_010_ARGParam_Variable
    Migration of ARG parameters path variable from ${workspace_dir} to ${eclipse.workspace}.
    Task_011_EvidenceNoAssessable
    Deletion of evidence without an assessable (PCMM Element or Subelement).
